"><div class="media-object-rich-text"><h4>更多食品和饮料</h4><ul class="articleList"><li><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/blue-crab-recipe-this-3-ingredient-feast-is-a-summer-weekend-showstopper-6f58784d?mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">螃蟹、玉米、黄油：这三种食材的盛宴是夏季周末的亮点</a></li><li><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/cocktail-ratios-for-easy-drinks-at-home-4b4b9c36?mod=article_relatedinline&amp;mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">记住这些鸡尾酒比例，以便在家轻松饮用</a></li><li><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/crab-risotto-recipe-worthy-of-sophia-loren-bb330842?mod=article_relatedinline&amp;mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">这道快捷蟹肉烩饭是值得索菲亚·罗兰 (Sophia Loren) 的夏日食谱</a></li><li><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/grilled-calamari-recipe-e7196b17?mod=article_relatedinline&amp;mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">在烧烤车辙中？这道海鲜快餐就是答案</a></li><li><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/for-healthy-vietnamese-recipes-this-gen-x-chef-consulted-a-master-mom-39d9d919?mod=article_relatedinline&amp;mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">对于健康的越南食谱，这位 X 世代厨师咨询了一位大师：妈妈</a></li></ul></div></div></section></div></main></div>]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 27 Jul 2023 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.wsj.com/articles/one-glass-of-wine-a-day-64ead6a9</guid><link/> https://www.wsj.com/articles/one-glass-of-wine-a-day-64ead6a9<author><![CDATA[Lettie Teague]]></author><category>下班</category><category>政治/一般新闻</category><category>食物和饮料</category><category>生活/生活方式</category><category>SYND</category><category>华尔街日报-PRO-WSJ.com</category><category>政治的</category><category>一般新闻</category><category>食物</category><category>喝</category><category>活的</category><category>生活方式</category></item></channel></rss>